                <img src="/upload/FAD/Ingresssbilder/OEP_100x75.jpg" alt="" class="ArticleImg" />
            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/fad/press-centre/press-releases/2010/Every-citizen-now-able-to-look-public-authorities-in-the-cards.html?id=605000" title="">
                        Every citizen now able to look public authorities in the cards
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[18.05.2010]</p>
                <p>A public electronic post journal for the civil service (OEP) is launched as the first of its kind in the world.   – From this day on everyone is able to get access to the documents of the central civil service. Until now, only journalists had the right to do so. OEP is democracy and openness in practice, reform minister Rigmor Aasrud says. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
