                <img src="/upload/FAD/Ingresssbilder/svalbard_100x75.jpg" alt="Longyearbyen, Spitsbergen. Photo: Stian Danenbarger (Creative Commons)" class="ArticleImg" />
            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/fad/press-centre/press-releases/2008/competition-law-being-enforced-on-spitsb.html?id=519317" title="">
                        Competition Law being enforced on Svalbard
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[25.06.2008]</p>
                <p>While many complain about having to deal with too many laws and regulations, the inhabitants on Svalbard (Spitsbergen) are complaining that they have too few of them. For one thing, they would like to see the Norwegian Competition Law enforced on Spitsbergen as well. Now the Norwegian government is going to fulfill that wish.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
