                        Reports on improving the performance of competition policy
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[05.12.2007]</p>
                <p>The Ministry has received the reports from two external R&D-projects being part of the work to improve the performance of the competition policy.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
